{"word":"G1257 - διαλείπω - dialeípō - dee-al-i'-po - Cease","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαλείπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dialeípō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-al-i'-po</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cease</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒய்வு"},{"paragraph":"to interpose a delay, to intermit, leave off for a time something already begun"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G3007 - λείπω - leípō - li'-po/3007\">G3007</a>; to <i>leave off in the middle</i>, that is, <i>intermit:</i> - cease.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1257/1257\">G1257</a>, <a href=\"#/G2640/2640\">G2640</a>, <a href=\"#/G2641/2641\">G2641</a>, <a href=\"#/G3005/3005\">G3005</a>, <a href=\"#/G4035/4035\">G4035</a>"}]}